Package com.cafean.client.ui.diff

Class CategoryGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.ui.diff.CategoryGroup
  • public class CategoryGroup
extends java.lang.Object
    A logical grouping of components by category for the MultiComponentDiffViewer. Lists of components for the left and right component selections are maintained with an index corresponding to each component on each side. CategoryGroups can be sorted by Category and CCNumber, or simply by Category.

    • Method Detail

      • sort

        public void sort​(boolean sortByCCNumber)
        Sorts the elements in this group. If sortByCCNumber is true, components are sorted by category and ccnumber, and only components that have the same ccnumber can line up(appear in the same diff table row). Otherwise, components are sorted by category only, and components with different ccnumbers can line up.
        Parameters:
        sortByCCNumber -
